boomers retirements to later generations 
this smacks a little bit of the reagan philosophy which can 
be summed up as dont visit your grandchildren just send them the 
bill says rep andrew jacobs dind chairman of the house 
ways and means social security subcommittee 
but the proposal could be irresistible to lawmakers who love a 
chance to cut taxes 
weve been called by offices from both sides of the aisle 
says lobbyist judy schub of the american association of retired 
persons which so far has shied away from moynihans plan its 
got a lot of appeal 
