23 since last january about 20 bills have been spawned excluding 
the social security trust fund from deficit calculations 
many concede the political appeal of the offbudget proposals is 
probably unstoppable in a measure of the ideas appeal the white 
house says president bush will include a version of the plan in the 
fiscal 1991 budget he presents congress on jan 29 
