dismissed and another 10000 for invalids pap said about 10000 
will be offered small loans to start private businesses 
the fund also will provide equalizing payments for 50000 
workers who lose their jobs due to group dismissals or are forced 
to accept lower paying jobs 
the fund relies on mandatory contributions from workplaces but 
the state will step in with contributions from the budget if more 
funds are needed the agency said 
