would be spread throughout the year and occur through layoffs 
attrition and selling off businesses the firm announced plans for 
acrosstheboard trimming in november 
yager said the firm had no target for the size reductions but a 
merrill official speaking on condition of anonymity said the 
reductions would total about 3000 including as many as 1000 
layoffs 
we are going through a selective process and there will be 
selective layoffs as we go along yager said 
