lawyers for a business newsletter say a court 
order preventing publication of an article about the big six 
accounting firm ernst amp young violates freedom of the press 
the order issued jan 8 by new york supreme court judge 
beatrice shainswit bars bowmans accounting report a newsletter 
based in atlanta from disclosing confidential or proprietary 
information on ernst amp young 
the article planned for the front page of the january edition 
was to have analyzed the merger in june of ernst amp whinney and 
arthur young a story the newsletter broke in may 
