called the order a major first amendment issue this is an 
unconstitutional prior restraint 
but carl liggio general counsel for ernst amp young said the 
issue has nothing to do with prior restraint 
he can write any stories he wants but he cant make use of 
confidential information in any manner shape or form liggio 
said 
