fourth quarter and year tuesday reflecting strength in their 
corporate and consumer finance businesses and weakness caused by 
shaky real estate loans and third world debt 
severe quarterly declines were reported by citicorp 
manufacturers hanover corp and mellon bank corp while security 
pacific corp and wells fargo amp co reported big earnings increases 
