federated holding company but he will phase out his 
responsibilities at the canadian parent 
john w burden iii chairman and chief executive officer of 
federated and allied has quit effective jan 31 to pursue other 
interests campeau said the company said it expects to announce 
a successor soon to run the retailing operations 
james m zimmerman will remain as president and chief operating 
officer of federated and allied the management teams at all 
department store chains will continue in place 
chapter 11 grants the companies a reprieve from creditors 
lawsuits while they formulate a plan to repay their debts all 
financial decisions for the companies must now be approved by us 
bankruptcy judge j vincent aug he declined to comment on the case 
federateds stores include abraham and straus and bloomingdales 
of new york burdines of miami lazarus of cincinnati and richs 
of atlanta 
allieds stores include the bon marche of seattle jordan marsh 
of boston maas brothers of tampa and sterns of paramus nj 
